      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAGPIE HARRY (5) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by half a length at this track in a handy 23.24 beating Bonded. The form out of his last race has been franked. Can go close again if runs up to latest figure. DOT'S REDEEMER (8) comes off an average effort last start when eighth at this track over 400m behind Paw Uella (23.82) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Key runner on best form. ON SONG ICE (1) goes very well this course and distance starting 12 times for four wins and two minors. Was out of the placings last time (22.91) at this track in a Grade 4/5, finishing fifth and beaten 6 lengths. Can feature with the right run. INGA BUDDY (4) is right in the mix.",
